1.在mysql创建表导入数据

2.创建目录

创建本地状态文件  
mkdir -p /var/lib/flume  
cd /var/lib/flume  
touch sql-source.status  
chmod -R 777 /var/lib/flume

创建hdfs目录  
hdfs dfs -mkdir -p /flume/mysql  
hdfs dfs -chmod -R 777 /flume/mysql

3.配置flume

option3文件如下：

    
    
    a1.sources = r1
    a1.sinks = k1 k2
    a1.channels = c1  c2
    
    a1.sources.r1.channels = c1 c2
    a1.sources.r1.type= org.keedio.flume.source.SQLSource
    a1.sources.r1.connection.url = jdbc:mysql://node1:3306/test
    a1.sources.r1.user = root
    a1.sources.r1.password = 123
    a1.sources.r1.autocommit = true
    a1.sources.r1.dialect = org.hibernate.dialect.MySQL5Dialect
    a1.sources.r1.driver_class =  com.mysql.jdbc.Driver
    a1.sources.r1.table = wlslog
    a1.sources.r1.columns.to.select = *
    a1.sources.r1.incremental.column.name = id 
    a1.sources.r1.incremental.value = 0
    a1.sources.r1.run.query.delay=5000
    a1.sources.r1.status.file.path = /var/lib/flume  
    a1.sources.r1.status.file.name = sql-source.status  
    
    #配置hdfs sink
    a1.sinks.k1.channel = c1
    a1.sinks.k1.type = hdfs
    a1.sinks.k1.hdfs.path = hdfs://mycluster/flume/mysql
    a1.sinks.k1.hdfs.fileType = DataStream
    a1.sinks.k1.hdfs.writeFormat = Text
    a1.sinks.k1.hdfs.rollSize = 268435456
    a1.sinks.k1.hdfs.rollInterval = 0
    a1.sinks.k1.hdfs.rollCount = 0
    
    #c1
    a1.channels.c1.type = memory
    a1.channels.c1.capacity = 1000
    a1.channels.c1.transactionCapacity = 100
    
    #c2
    a1.channels.c2.type = memory
    a1.channels.c2.capacity = 1000
    a1.channels.c2.transactionCapacity = 100
    
    #配置kafka
    a1.sinks.k2.type = org.apache.flume.sink.kafka.KafkaSink
    a1.sinks.k2.channel = c2
    a1.sinks.k2.brokerList=node1:9092,node2:9092,node3:9092
    a1.sinks.k2.topic=test
    a1.sinks.k2.requiredAcks = 1
    a1.sinks.k2.batchSize = 2
    a1.sinks.k2.channel = c2

4.准备JAR包

在 /usr/local/apache-flume-1.6.0-bin/lib加入flume-ng-sql-source-1.3.7.jar和mysql-
connector-java-5.1.32-bin.jar

5.启动kafka消费者

bin/kafka-console-consumer.sh --zookeeper node2:2181,node3:2181,node4:2181
--from-beginning --topic test

6.启动flume-ng agent --conf-file option3 --name a1
-Dflume.root.logger=INFO,console

可以看到数据已经采集成功

![](data:image/png;base64,)

通过轮询的方式实现增量，只能做到准实时，而且轮询间隔越短，对源库的影响越大。  
只能识别新增数据，检测不到删除与更新。  
要求mysql必须有用于表示增量的字段。  

11.数据加载到hive中

启动hive：hive --service metastore

建立外部表指定location

    
    
    create EXTERNAL table ext_wlslog
    (
    id string,
    time_stamp string,
    category string,
    type string,
    servername string,
    code string,
    msg string
    )
    ROW FORMAT DELIMITED 
    FIELDS TERMINATED BY ','
    LINES TERMINATED BY '\n'
    LOCATION '/usr/'

加载数据：load data inpath '/flume/mysql' into table ext_wlslog;

使用load加载数据，如果建表的时候指定了location位置hdfs数据文件会移动到LOCATION '/usr/'；

不指定location位置默认会移动到hive_remote/warehouse/下

![](data:image/png;base64,)
